metadata.name: Bayside Toolbox #1
metadata.description:
The Toolbox is your access pass into the world of Bayside and a rare collectible crafted by Fortress, the finest tool builder in the Metaverse.

But what will it be used for? This digital collectible is critical to unlock goods and pair alongside items that sit behind the bar. Not to mention the night is coming, and our barkeep needs your help to get things ready.
